1
00:01:35,150 --> 00:01:41,310
[Goodbye My Princess]

2
00:01:41,310 --> 00:01:44,230
[Episode 1]

3
00:02:48,740 --> 00:02:52,020
I've known him for 30 years.

4
00:02:54,570 --> 00:03:00,740
Thirty years... long enough for someone to become a successful candidate in the highest imperial examination and for a general to return to the imperial court after a long battle.

5
00:03:00,740 --> 00:03:05,580
Even I, myself, now have a big chubby grandson.

6
00:03:07,470 --> 00:03:13,960
But he... spent 30 years in searching for a place.

7
00:03:17,320 --> 00:03:24,040
A legend in the Western Border says "Immerse oneself in the River of Oblivion to forget."

8
00:03:24,040 --> 00:03:29,980
Jump into the River of Oblivion and all troubles will be forgotten.

9
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:47,910
Maybe god's punishment to people is not to forget,

10
00:03:47,910 --> 00:03:52,330
but to always remember.

11
00:04:15,570 --> 00:04:18,310
Hurry, take Dimo and go find the physician to examine her.

12
00:04:18,310 --> 00:04:19,850
Yes.

13
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:21,720
Where is my teacher?

14
00:04:21,720 --> 00:04:24,670
Noble Warrior Gu should be at the site for the celebration of the Double Seventh Festival (Chinese Valentine's Day).

15
00:04:24,670 --> 00:04:27,440
- Let me know when Dimo is awake.
- Yes.

16
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:45,780
Mingyuan, will there be any songs and dances for the celebration of this festival?

17
00:04:45,780 --> 00:04:49,500
Your Majesty, songs and dances will start after sunset.

18
00:04:49,500 --> 00:04:52,480
When the moon rises, during the worship of the Goddess of the Weaver (From the legend "The Cowherd and the Girl Weaver," the couple could meet in the Milky Way only once a year),

19
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:54,760
all the lanterns will rise up everywhere.

20
00:04:54,760 --> 00:04:58,260
Together, the sky and the stars will shine. It will be spectacular!

21
00:04:58,260 --> 00:05:01,380
I didn't expect that the Double Seventh Festival from the Central Plains,

22
00:05:01,380 --> 00:05:04,540
when it came to this Yanzhi City of Xi State,

23
00:05:04,540 --> 00:05:08,000
could be so distinctive and it's worth looking forward to.

24
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:10,570
Festivities from Central Plains are not that desirable.

25
00:05:10,570 --> 00:05:14,520
It involves so many people and wastes money.

26
00:05:19,250 --> 00:05:21,080
Please move aside.

27
00:05:27,620 --> 00:05:29,440
Teacher!

28
00:05:29,950 --> 00:05:31,910
Xiaofeng?

29
00:05:31,910 --> 00:05:34,020
Dad, Mom, Consort Mingyuan.

30
00:05:34,020 --> 00:05:35,980
Xiaofeng!

31
00:05:35,980 --> 00:05:37,710
Look at yourself. So unpresentable!

32
00:05:37,710 --> 00:05:39,420
I have to find Teacher for an urgent matter.

33
00:05:39,420 --> 00:05:41,900
I will come back later to greet all of you.

34
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:47,060
This child! You have spoiled her.

35
00:05:47,060 --> 00:05:49,210
Why is it my fault?

36
00:05:49,210 --> 00:05:51,570
All-day long, spending time with Xiaofeng...

37
00:05:51,570 --> 00:05:54,040
is that teacher from Central Plains.

38
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:58,180
I say, it is that teacher who has misled her.

39
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:03,290
Your Majesty, I have seen enough here.

40
00:06:03,290 --> 00:06:05,740
Should we leave?

41
00:06:06,880 --> 00:06:09,190
Mingyuan.

42
00:06:09,190 --> 00:06:11,820
I will return to the palace when I finish the decoration here.

43
00:06:13,170 --> 00:06:16,440
Goodbye! Your Majesty and My Queen.

44
00:06:24,670 --> 00:06:27,790
Teacher! Teacher!

45
00:06:28,550 --> 00:06:30,480
Something has happened! A major thing has happened!

46
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:33,910
Something major has happened? Tell me about it.

47
00:06:33,910 --> 00:06:35,420
I found the River of Oblivion.

48
00:06:35,420 --> 00:06:37,760
River of Oblivion?

49
00:06:37,760 --> 00:06:40,070
Why? You don't believe me?

50
00:06:40,610 --> 00:06:42,520
Here! This is water from the River of Oblivion.

51
00:06:42,520 --> 00:06:45,580
I filled it myself. It's a hundred percent real.

52
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:48,660
Water from the River of Oblivion?

53
00:06:48,660 --> 00:06:52,430
It's true! A moment ago, Dimo fell into the river and drank some water.

54
00:06:52,430 --> 00:06:55,100
Now, she doesn't remember anything.

55
00:06:56,290 --> 00:06:59,890
You can't drink that! I told you it's the water from the River of Oblivion! Why would you still drink it?

56
00:06:59,890 --> 00:07:02,140
If I don't try it, how do I know if it's water from the River of Oblivion?

57
00:07:02,140 --> 00:07:04,580
Oh, no-no-no! You'll forget about me!

58
00:07:04,580 --> 00:07:06,890
Hurry and spit it out, Teacher!

59
00:07:06,890 --> 00:07:08,550
Hurry and spit it out, Teacher!

60
00:07:08,550 --> 00:07:10,650
You can't drink it, Teacher!

61
00:07:10,650 --> 00:07:11,960
Teacher!

62
00:07:11,960 --> 00:07:15,260
I told you it was the water from the River of Oblivion! If you drink it, you'll forget me!

63
00:07:15,260 --> 00:07:18,700
- Why would you still drink it?! Hurry and spit it out!
- My head really hurts.

64
00:07:22,050 --> 00:07:23,740
Teacher.

65
00:07:29,190 --> 00:07:30,830
Teacher?

66
00:07:31,520 --> 00:07:33,980
Do you still remember me?

67
00:07:35,620 --> 00:07:39,690
Oh, no-no-no!

68
00:07:41,260 --> 00:07:43,940
Princess!

69
00:07:43,940 --> 00:07:45,750
Princess!

70
00:07:47,250 --> 00:07:48,190
Dimo!

71
00:07:48,190 --> 00:07:49,850
Princess, the imperial doctor said

72
00:07:49,850 --> 00:07:52,180
I only hit my head and fainted.

73
00:07:52,180 --> 00:07:54,940
Look, I'm fine now.

74
00:07:54,940 --> 00:07:57,330
You remember me?

75
00:07:57,330 --> 00:07:59,290
You're all right?

76
00:08:03,210 --> 00:08:05,120
You lied to me!

77
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:08,200
Silly girl, how could you find water from the River of Oblivion so easily?

78
00:08:08,200 --> 00:08:10,900
If I say that it's the River of Oblivion, then it is. I'll name it the River of Oblivion!

79
00:08:10,900 --> 00:08:12,970
- It's called the River of Oblivion!
- All right.

80
00:08:12,970 --> 00:08:15,700
If you say its called the River of Oblivion, then it is.

81
00:08:15,700 --> 00:08:19,280
But this River of Oblivion is not that River of Oblivion.

82
00:08:29,810 --> 00:08:31,950
Consort Mingyuan!

83
00:08:38,260 --> 00:08:39,510
My Lady!

84
00:08:39,510 --> 00:08:42,760
My Lady!

85
00:08:42,760 --> 00:08:44,460
My Lady!

86
00:08:46,020 --> 00:08:48,340
Hurry and get the imperial doctor!

87
00:08:52,730 --> 00:08:54,520
I will leave now.

88
00:09:00,860 --> 00:09:04,470
Your Majesty, her physical injury is minor.

89
00:09:04,470 --> 00:09:07,580
But her symptoms

90
00:09:07,580 --> 00:09:11,150
suggest that she has consumption.

91
00:09:11,150 --> 00:09:13,320
- Consumption?
- Yes.

92
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:15,420
That would mean...

93
00:09:16,430 --> 00:09:17,670
You may leave.

94
00:09:17,670 --> 00:09:19,740
Yes, Your Majesty.

95
00:09:28,350 --> 00:09:30,150
Your Majesty.

96
00:09:37,460 --> 00:09:40,610
Don't listen to him. The doctor is wrong.

97
00:09:40,610 --> 00:09:42,340
Rest well.

98
00:09:42,340 --> 00:09:44,080
The festival in a few days

99
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:47,380
is dependent on you to host. When you get better,

100
00:09:47,380 --> 00:09:49,790
the Zhaohe, next year, I'll go to myself.

101
00:09:49,790 --> 00:09:51,640
And I'll go with you to the imperial city.

102
00:09:51,640 --> 00:09:55,310
You will get a good chance to look around your hometown.

103
00:09:56,890 --> 00:10:00,920
I appreciate how well Your Majesty has treated me.

104
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:05,420
After the previous king passed away, I remarried you.

105
00:10:05,420 --> 00:10:08,250
Although I'm underneath the queen,

106
00:10:08,250 --> 00:10:11,340
you never treated me with less.

107
00:10:11,340 --> 00:10:15,970
Without your good favor,

108
00:10:15,970 --> 00:10:18,510
the fact that I was on my second marriage

109
00:10:18,510 --> 00:10:22,000
would've embarrassed me too much to keep living in the palace.

110
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:24,190
You obviously know

111
00:10:24,190 --> 00:10:26,940
I never cared about that. If it wasn't for you,

112
00:10:26,940 --> 00:10:30,740
there would be war in Xi State instead of peace.

113
00:10:30,740 --> 00:10:35,110
The people of Xi State and I thank you.

114
00:10:37,890 --> 00:10:43,450
But... if I die,

115
00:10:43,450 --> 00:10:46,700
Your Majesty would be caught again

116
00:10:46,700 --> 00:10:49,920
between Danchi and the Li Empire.

117
00:10:56,700 --> 00:10:58,870
If Xiaofeng

118
00:10:59,870 --> 00:11:04,230
can marry the crown prince of Li Empire and become the crown princess,

119
00:11:04,230 --> 00:11:08,360
she will one day become the empress

120
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:14,500
and her son will have the blood of Danchi and Xi State.

121
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:21,670
Your Majesty, I married you.

122
00:11:21,670 --> 00:11:25,720
I know you and the queen don't want to marry Xiaofeng far.

123
00:11:25,720 --> 00:11:27,460
But...

124
00:11:28,620 --> 00:11:32,360
the people of the two countries are finally enjoying their peace.

125
00:11:32,360 --> 00:11:36,760
If they get ravaged by war again,

126
00:11:36,760 --> 00:11:39,550
it will break my heart.

127
00:11:39,550 --> 00:11:42,770
I want to establish more than

128
00:11:42,770 --> 00:11:45,220
a Chinese Valentine's festival in Xi State.

129
00:11:45,220 --> 00:11:50,080
I want the two countries to be on a hundred years of good terms.

130
00:11:52,390 --> 00:11:54,020
All right.

131
00:11:54,770 --> 00:11:59,840
I agree to the marriage between Xiaofeng and the Li Empire.

132
00:12:06,310 --> 00:12:08,280
What?

133
00:12:09,150 --> 00:12:11,810
Marriage?

134
00:12:11,810 --> 00:12:13,590
His Majesty agreed?

135
00:12:13,590 --> 00:12:17,270
Absolutely. I heard it with my own ears.

136
00:12:20,780 --> 00:12:23,020
The crown prince of Li Empire is not here yet.

137
00:12:23,020 --> 00:12:26,400
Whatever His Majesty agreed to is only an empty promise.

138
00:12:26,400 --> 00:12:28,800
Xiaofeng is my daughter.

139
00:12:29,840 --> 00:12:35,520
That Chinese woman has no say in her marriage.

140
00:12:35,520 --> 00:12:38,030
I will never let Xiaofeng

141
00:12:38,030 --> 00:12:40,510
marry into the Li Empire.

142
00:12:41,880 --> 00:12:43,020
Get me paper and a pen.

143
00:12:43,020 --> 00:12:44,500
Yes.

144
00:13:52,180 --> 00:13:54,730
Hey!

145
00:13:54,730 --> 00:13:56,960
Hey!

146
00:14:09,210 --> 00:14:11,110
Khan!

147
00:14:13,190 --> 00:14:17,410
Khan, Princess Ashinayun sent you a letter from Xi State.

148
00:14:32,700 --> 00:14:36,220
Your sister A'Du is friendly with Xiaofeng, and she has good fighting skills.

149
00:14:36,220 --> 00:14:37,960
Send A'Du to Xi State.

150
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:41,740
She can help without triggering suspicion.

151
00:14:41,740 --> 00:14:43,270
Understood.

152
00:14:50,650 --> 00:14:52,460
Report!

153
00:14:53,380 --> 00:14:56,410
My King, the informant from Xi State sent news.

154
00:15:07,790 --> 00:15:11,990
Who knew the dying Consort Mingyuan tried to get

155
00:15:11,990 --> 00:15:17,370
Qu Wencheng to marry his daughter to the Li Empire.

156
00:15:21,970 --> 00:15:24,880
If Li Empire wants a joint union with Xi State,

157
00:15:24,880 --> 00:15:27,870
so can Shuobo.

158
00:15:27,870 --> 00:15:31,750
My King, if you married the ninth princess,

159
00:15:31,750 --> 00:15:35,810
we may get all the economic support from Xi State with trading.

160
00:15:35,810 --> 00:15:39,090
As for the military, Danchi will also support us.

161
00:15:39,090 --> 00:15:43,370
Then, we will no longer be limited by others.

162
00:15:45,690 --> 00:15:48,520
That makes good sense.

163
00:15:48,520 --> 00:15:51,200
Lidun, go to Xi State immediately

164
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:54,900
and offer marriage for me to the ninth princess.

165
00:15:54,900 --> 00:15:56,800
Understood.

166
00:16:31,320 --> 00:16:35,430
[Eastern Palace]

167
00:16:38,140 --> 00:16:41,410
Li Chengji, you horrible child.

168
00:16:41,410 --> 00:16:44,850
How dare you wear funeral clothes in the palace!

169
00:16:44,850 --> 00:16:46,550
You are trying to curse me

170
00:16:46,550 --> 00:16:49,920
because you can't wait take my place?

171
00:16:49,920 --> 00:16:51,420
Father,

172
00:16:51,420 --> 00:16:54,150
the public knows that you, Father, love the country.

173
00:16:54,150 --> 00:16:56,860
And you love the ordinary citizens as your own parents. I'm wearing the mourning apparel

174
00:16:56,860 --> 00:17:00,300
to offer my condolence to the seven imperial exam candidates who were wronged and driven to death.

175
00:17:00,300 --> 00:17:03,320
The case is closed by the Court of Judicial Review.

176
00:17:03,320 --> 00:17:05,980
Don't bring it up again.

177
00:17:05,980 --> 00:17:09,890
Emperor Father, "Only those under the roof know there's a leakage; only the court and the commonality know when there's misgovernance."

178
00:17:09,890 --> 00:17:14,330
As the head proctor, Gao Yuming violated the law and disrupted the exam system by buying and selling court positions.

179
00:17:14,330 --> 00:17:17,380
He allowed countless mediocre or useless candidates to serve in the government.

180
00:17:17,380 --> 00:17:20,970
Those that were truly talented scholars

181
00:17:20,970 --> 00:17:22,870
were rejected from the government without appeal

182
00:17:22,870 --> 00:17:25,900
solely due to Gao Yuming's self-interest.

183
00:17:25,900 --> 00:17:29,990
How can Father let the Court of Judicial Review carelessly close the case?

184
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:32,930
You said Minister Gao violated the law

185
00:17:32,930 --> 00:17:36,360
and disrupted the exam system. What is your proof?

186
00:17:36,360 --> 00:17:39,340
Those dead test takers are the proof.

187
00:17:39,340 --> 00:17:42,360
Do you know that those seven test-takers'

188
00:17:42,360 --> 00:17:46,380
families had signed a statement

189
00:17:46,380 --> 00:17:48,230
testifying

190
00:17:48,230 --> 00:17:51,230
this matter is unrelated to Minister Gao.

191
00:17:51,230 --> 00:17:56,570
Those test-takers that you mentioned, who had nowhere to redress,

192
00:17:56,570 --> 00:17:59,090
said you were the one

193
00:17:59,090 --> 00:18:03,190
who ordered them to frame Minister Gao.

194
00:18:03,190 --> 00:18:06,060
There are mountains of complaints filed against you.

195
00:18:06,060 --> 00:18:11,390
The court officials are accusing you of wrongdoing and framing loyal officials.

196
00:18:11,980 --> 00:18:15,360
Father, everything I said is the truth. It's Minister Gao!

197
00:18:15,360 --> 00:18:18,160
Minister Gao had bribed them. Please investigate this matter, Father.

198
00:18:18,160 --> 00:18:19,920
You are aggravatingly stubborn.

199
00:18:19,920 --> 00:18:22,260
I order you to stay

200
00:18:22,260 --> 00:18:24,580
inside the palace and think the matter over.

201
00:18:24,580 --> 00:18:26,620
You are forbidden to join in the affairs of the state.

202
00:18:26,620 --> 00:18:30,380
Emperor Father, "People are the foundation of the country; only when the foundation is firm will the country be peaceful."

203
00:18:30,380 --> 00:18:33,530
If even you are blinded by those who ignore the law of the land,

204
00:18:33,530 --> 00:18:36,440
allowing them to violate the rules and shake the country's foundation,

205
00:18:36,440 --> 00:18:40,220
one day we will lose the heart of the people; and therefore, the country.

206
00:18:40,220 --> 00:18:42,450
Are you trying to teach me to rule the country?

207
00:18:42,450 --> 00:18:45,210
- You are not in a place to do so!
- Father!

208
00:18:45,210 --> 00:18:48,620
Come! Bring me the whip!

209
00:18:59,980 --> 00:19:04,410
Father, you had taught me since I was a child

210
00:19:04,410 --> 00:19:07,020
that I should live up to the people; to society.

211
00:19:07,020 --> 00:19:09,840
If I can't even protect the people as the crown prince of Li Empire,

212
00:19:09,840 --> 00:19:12,200
how will I ever protect the Li Empire?

213
00:19:12,200 --> 00:19:18,220
Father, please investigate the issue and restore justice to those test-takers.

214
00:19:18,220 --> 00:19:20,210
Stop recording!

215
00:19:21,480 --> 00:19:25,170
This is a family matter. You don't need to record it.

216
00:19:25,170 --> 00:19:29,460
Your Majesty's family matter is also state matter.

217
00:19:38,580 --> 00:19:40,410
You listen up.

218
00:19:40,410 --> 00:19:43,200
If you still want to safely be a crown prince,

219
00:19:43,200 --> 00:19:46,460
then take off your mourning clothes right now

220
00:19:46,460 --> 00:19:48,350
and never mention the case again.

221
00:19:48,350 --> 00:19:51,660
I've been a safe crown prince for more than 20 years.

222
00:19:51,660 --> 00:19:54,630
I've never said "no" to you, Father.

223
00:19:54,630 --> 00:19:57,690
I don't have your cold-bloodedness, Father.

224
00:19:57,690 --> 00:20:00,520
I can't allow those test-takers to die for nothing.

225
00:20:00,520 --> 00:20:03,970
I don't understand why you don't want to clear up the case.

226
00:20:03,970 --> 00:20:06,890
Are you ignoring the laws so you can protect those criminals?

227
00:20:06,890 --> 00:20:09,830
Do you really want to be known as the fatuous emperor by history?

228
00:20:09,830 --> 00:20:11,950
You, unfilial son!

229
00:20:16,140 --> 00:20:17,940
Father, he is only acting from a moment of impulse.

230
00:20:17,940 --> 00:20:20,130
Shut up! A word more from you and

231
00:20:20,130 --> 00:20:23,460
- I'll punish you with him!
- Father!

232
00:20:23,460 --> 00:20:25,190
Don't waste your time defending me.

233
00:20:25,190 --> 00:20:28,330
Father is being arbitrary. He doesn't want to know the truth.

234
00:20:28,330 --> 00:20:31,720
Maybe when the party of Gao has taken over the Li Empire,

235
00:20:31,720 --> 00:20:34,260
he will finally understand what I'm saying.

236
00:20:34,260 --> 00:20:37,580
I'll kill you today!

237
00:20:41,520 --> 00:20:43,980
No, Father!

238
00:20:49,920 --> 00:20:51,810
Why are you laughing?

239
00:20:52,570 --> 00:20:57,980
I'm laughing because there will be another foolish ruler who kills his son.

240
00:20:57,980 --> 00:21:00,980
Your Majesty!

241
00:21:01,960 --> 00:21:03,750
Your Majesty!

242
00:21:05,020 --> 00:21:08,660
Your Majesty, urgent news from Xi State.

243
00:21:12,000 --> 00:21:14,310
Your Majesty,

244
00:21:14,310 --> 00:21:19,290
I recommend Prince of Xuande as ambassador to propose marriage to the Xi State.

245
00:21:19,290 --> 00:21:23,370
For one, he can investigate the true strength within the Xi State;

246
00:21:23,370 --> 00:21:26,190
and thus, ensure the security of our border.

247
00:21:26,190 --> 00:21:29,220
Second, by sending a prince,

248
00:21:29,220 --> 00:21:33,340
he demonstrates the sincerity of our marriage proposal.

249
00:21:33,340 --> 00:21:37,440
Third, Prince of Xuade can represent Your Majesty

250
00:21:37,440 --> 00:21:41,570
to visit Princess Mingyuan.

251
00:22:07,460 --> 00:22:10,690
Your Majesty.

252
00:22:10,690 --> 00:22:13,500
Minister Gao, waive the formality. You are not well enough.

253
00:22:13,500 --> 00:22:15,460
Have a seat. Cao Ji.

254
00:22:15,460 --> 00:22:17,960
In my opinion,

255
00:22:17,960 --> 00:22:22,220
to have Prince of Xuande go when the crown prince is available

256
00:22:22,220 --> 00:22:25,360
might break the rules.

257
00:22:25,360 --> 00:22:29,370
It will make the foreigners look down on us.

258
00:22:29,370 --> 00:22:34,140
The crown prince is morally lacking and will not be suitable for the task.

259
00:22:34,140 --> 00:22:36,520
Please watch what you say.

260
00:22:36,520 --> 00:22:38,860
There is nothing to hide.

261
00:22:38,860 --> 00:22:43,710
Everyone here knows the crown prince is connected to the test-taker case.

262
00:22:43,710 --> 00:22:48,200
The case is still under investigation. There is no verdict yet.

263
00:22:49,730 --> 00:22:54,140
Today, in the Eastern Palace, His Majesty had used family punishment.

264
00:22:54,140 --> 00:22:59,280
The emperor is planning to abolish the crown prince.

265
00:23:00,790 --> 00:23:05,440
Prince of Zhong, you are very well informed.

266
00:23:07,360 --> 00:23:11,110
I apologize.

267
00:23:11,110 --> 00:23:13,640
Brother, take care of yourself.

268
00:23:13,640 --> 00:23:15,820
When Father isn't so angry, he will understand.

269
00:23:15,820 --> 00:23:18,200
He will give you the justice you seek.

270
00:23:25,130 --> 00:23:29,400
Fifth Brother, is it not clear to you?

271
00:23:31,100 --> 00:23:34,440
Father is a very sharp person.

272
00:23:34,440 --> 00:23:37,070
I didn't do what a crown prince should do.

273
00:23:37,070 --> 00:23:40,400
Then, he must do what an emperor should do.

274
00:23:42,620 --> 00:23:45,560
He has been disappointed by me for a long time already.

275
00:23:45,560 --> 00:23:47,370
No.

276
00:23:47,370 --> 00:23:49,780
Brother, you have always been generous and diligent.

277
00:23:49,780 --> 00:23:51,650
You are the role model for us brothers.

278
00:23:51,650 --> 00:23:55,330
Father often relies on you. How could he be disappointed by you?

279
00:23:55,330 --> 00:23:58,420
Brother, maybe you don't know.

280
00:23:58,420 --> 00:24:01,110
Since I was a child, I have envied you the most.

281
00:24:01,880 --> 00:24:03,760
Not because you are the crown prince,

282
00:24:03,760 --> 00:24:09,960
but because Father acts like a regular father whenever he looks at you.

283
00:24:12,100 --> 00:24:14,740
Father needs a wolf.

284
00:24:14,740 --> 00:24:19,640
And I am just an obedient dog.

285
00:24:19,640 --> 00:24:21,440
Brother!

286
00:24:25,130 --> 00:24:28,280
Do you know that

287
00:24:28,280 --> 00:24:32,350
the Eastern Palace is more dangerous than the palace?

288
00:24:32,350 --> 00:24:37,720
It is harder to be a crown prince than an emperor.

289
00:24:43,080 --> 00:24:44,900
Your Majesty.

290
00:24:46,820 --> 00:24:49,160
Marriage is the matter of the harem.

291
00:24:49,160 --> 00:24:51,460
My opinion as a woman

292
00:24:51,460 --> 00:24:56,120
is that the ninth princess of Xi State must be married to the crown prince.

293
00:24:56,120 --> 00:24:58,870
Whoever is the crown prince

294
00:24:58,870 --> 00:25:01,970
will always reside in the Eastern Palace.

295
00:25:01,970 --> 00:25:04,360
Why don't we send an ambassador

296
00:25:04,360 --> 00:25:06,890
to propose marriage in the name of Eastern Palace?

297
00:25:06,890 --> 00:25:10,220
It will avoid any confusion as a result of political instability.

298
00:25:11,330 --> 00:25:13,480
Your Majesty, I think...

299
00:25:13,480 --> 00:25:16,410
I have a suggestion.

300
00:25:16,410 --> 00:25:21,170
Minister Gao, I'm not finished yet.

301
00:25:22,190 --> 00:25:24,190
Please go ahead, Minister Gao.

302
00:25:28,830 --> 00:25:34,350
I recommend the crown prince lead the group to propose marriage to Xi State.

303
00:25:34,350 --> 00:25:37,910
The crown prince is young and rash. He got caught

304
00:25:37,910 --> 00:25:40,960
in the test-taking case by believing in false rumors.

305
00:25:40,960 --> 00:25:43,230
As a result, he had a misunderstanding regarding me.

306
00:25:43,230 --> 00:25:46,430
I am absolutely grateful that Your Majesty believes in me.

307
00:25:46,430 --> 00:25:50,530
As a father myself, I understand that the more we love them,

308
00:25:50,530 --> 00:25:53,550
the harsher we punish them.

309
00:25:53,550 --> 00:25:56,720
I ask Your Majesty to give the crown prince a chance to correct his wrong.

310
00:25:56,720 --> 00:26:00,690
If the crown prince can establish the marriage alliance,

311
00:26:00,690 --> 00:26:03,660
his accomplishment will

312
00:26:03,660 --> 00:26:07,660
silence the outrage in court.

313
00:26:13,470 --> 00:26:16,760
The crown prince lacks morals and cannot be a role model for court.

314
00:26:16,760 --> 00:26:21,010
He is thus abolished and demoted to Prince of Qin.

315
00:26:21,010 --> 00:26:24,360
But in consideration of the delicate situation in the Xi State,

316
00:26:24,360 --> 00:26:26,870
the order will not be publicly announced.

317
00:26:26,870 --> 00:26:29,530
You are ordered to depart in three days

318
00:26:29,530 --> 00:26:33,270
to visit Princess Mingyuan in Xi State.

319
00:26:33,270 --> 00:26:37,140
Lead the ambassadors to propose marriage to the princess of Xi State.

320
00:26:37,140 --> 00:26:40,530
Then immediately continue to the Western Border.

321
00:26:40,530 --> 00:26:45,040
You are not to return to the court until you garnered military merit!

322
00:26:48,550 --> 00:26:50,950
Your Majesty,

323
00:26:50,950 --> 00:26:55,720
aren't you being a bit harsh to the crown prince?

324
00:26:56,420 --> 00:27:00,140
I'm not being harsh to the crown prince.

325
00:27:00,140 --> 00:27:05,670
I'm being harsh on the future emperor of the Li Empire.

326
00:27:05,670 --> 00:27:07,940
If he can't sit securely in the Eastern Palace,

327
00:27:07,940 --> 00:27:13,690
how can he sit securely on the throne?

328
00:27:14,420 --> 00:27:16,590
Your Majesty is wise.

329
00:29:24,160 --> 00:29:26,340
Teacher!

330
00:30:24,400 --> 00:30:27,990
Teacher, help me!

331
00:30:31,250 --> 00:30:35,010
Teacher, help me!

332
00:30:57,410 --> 00:31:00,250
Master, look, this is what I won today.

333
00:31:00,250 --> 00:31:02,280
I am giving it to you.

334
00:31:04,970 --> 00:31:08,210
Do you know that in my Central Plains?

335
00:31:08,210 --> 00:31:12,620
If a woman gives a silk ball to a man, she then promises to marry him.

336
00:31:12,620 --> 00:31:14,240
Really?

337
00:31:14,240 --> 00:31:16,680
If it is Teacher, I will marry.

338
00:31:16,680 --> 00:31:19,200
Teacher, are you willing to marry me?

339
00:31:21,100 --> 00:31:23,040
Silly girl.

340
00:31:47,840 --> 00:31:49,230
Princess.

341
00:31:49,230 --> 00:31:51,230
Please don't stand on ceremony.

342
00:31:55,400 --> 00:31:57,680
Are you feeling better?

343
00:31:57,680 --> 00:32:00,510
My health has always been like this.

344
00:32:00,510 --> 00:32:03,570
Medicines don't seem to help.

345
00:32:03,570 --> 00:32:06,050
His Majesty has promised me

346
00:32:06,050 --> 00:32:09,770
to arrange a marital alliance between Xiaofeng and the Li Empire.

347
00:32:09,770 --> 00:32:12,370
Xiaofeng is the direct princess of the Xi State

348
00:32:12,370 --> 00:32:14,850
and she's the granddaughter of the King of Danchi.

349
00:32:14,850 --> 00:32:17,310
If she can marry into the Li Empire,

350
00:32:17,310 --> 00:32:21,250
that would keep the border at peace for several decades.

351
00:32:23,560 --> 00:32:27,260
Brother Mu, recently I saw Gu Jian and Xiaofeng.

352
00:32:27,260 --> 00:32:31,220
They are both young and innocent, and have fond feelings for each other.

353
00:32:31,220 --> 00:32:33,460
It's so enviable!

354
00:32:38,920 --> 00:32:44,390
However, they are burdened with different missions.

355
00:32:44,390 --> 00:32:46,700
Gu Jian is a good kid.

356
00:32:46,700 --> 00:32:50,350
You are his adoptive father. You should remind him

357
00:32:50,350 --> 00:32:53,800
not to fall into deep feelings.

358
00:32:53,800 --> 00:32:57,580
Otherwise, it can't be stopped once started.

359
00:33:02,510 --> 00:33:04,620
Please don't worry, Princess.

360
00:33:05,710 --> 00:33:09,000
I will not let Gu Jian step out of line.

361
00:33:20,600 --> 00:33:22,320
Fifth Brother.

362
00:33:23,790 --> 00:33:27,300
- I have a favor to ask you.
- Imperial Brother, please speak.

363
00:33:27,300 --> 00:33:30,240
Please help me send Grand Mentor out of the Capital.

364
00:33:30,240 --> 00:33:35,200
Let no one know his whereabouts, especially Prime Minister Gao.

365
00:33:35,200 --> 00:33:38,980
I know this is a dangerous move and I didn't want to get you involved.

366
00:33:38,980 --> 00:33:43,010
But under these exceptional circumstances, I can't even be sure of my own safety.

367
00:33:43,010 --> 00:33:45,940
I have no choice but to ask you to send him out of the city.

368
00:33:45,940 --> 00:33:49,190
I will fulfill the task you have entrusted to me.

369
00:34:06,860 --> 00:34:08,460
[Order]

370
00:34:08,460 --> 00:34:10,180
Your Highness!

371
00:34:10,180 --> 00:34:12,140
Let them go.

372
00:34:17,500 --> 00:34:20,080
Grand Mentor, I have made all the arrangements.

373
00:34:20,080 --> 00:34:23,790
Please take good care of yourself on the road.

374
00:34:23,790 --> 00:34:26,320
Imperial Brother wanted me to pass on a message to you, "The day is yet to come,

375
00:34:26,320 --> 00:34:29,820
the truth will reveal itself."

376
00:34:29,820 --> 00:34:35,490
I will never forget your great kindness.

377
00:34:35,490 --> 00:34:38,190
Please rise, Grand Mentor.

378
00:35:09,570 --> 00:35:13,790
I'm so indebted to you for your guidance, now that the crown prince is removed.

379
00:35:13,790 --> 00:35:16,690
Now I totally rely on you, Uncle,

380
00:35:16,690 --> 00:35:20,130
to help Chengyin enter the Eastern Palace.

381
00:35:21,630 --> 00:35:24,440
The new crown prince will be selected by His Imperial Majesty.

382
00:35:24,440 --> 00:35:28,340
Nothing can be accomplished by one stroke.

383
00:35:30,920 --> 00:35:33,790
Uncle, don't be so modest.

384
00:35:34,960 --> 00:35:37,990
For whoever can ascend to the position of crown prince,

385
00:35:37,990 --> 00:35:41,930
it's all under your complete control.

386
00:35:41,930 --> 00:35:45,440
Don't worry, Uncle. If Chengyin becomes the crown prince,

387
00:35:45,440 --> 00:35:49,560
my son and I will be grateful to you for your kindness.

388
00:35:49,560 --> 00:35:53,660
His Imperial Majesty abolished the crown prince and kept it in secret.

389
00:35:53,660 --> 00:35:56,420
Furthermore, he was assigned to the important task of managing the marriage alliance.

390
00:35:56,420 --> 00:36:00,660
Obviously, he is given another chance to earn a deed of merit,

391
00:36:00,660 --> 00:36:05,240
so as to let him gain prestige and trust in the court.

392
00:36:06,950 --> 00:36:10,650
To abolish and set up the crown prince

393
00:36:10,650 --> 00:36:13,900
is all at His Imperial Majesty's whim.

394
00:36:13,900 --> 00:36:17,210
Although the crown prince has lost favor from the emperor for the moment,

395
00:36:17,210 --> 00:36:22,040
if he could come back with accomplishment...

396
00:36:22,040 --> 00:36:27,630
Then don't even let him have the chance to be successful.

397
00:36:28,690 --> 00:36:31,620
There's one thing I still don't understand.

398
00:36:31,620 --> 00:36:35,100
Why did you suggest the crown prince go to the Xi State to propose marriage?

399
00:36:35,100 --> 00:36:39,000
If by any chance he returns with success and regains power, what should we do?

400
00:36:39,000 --> 00:36:42,640
Unfortunately, there will be no such chance.

401
00:36:42,640 --> 00:36:45,080
Fifth Prince arrives!

402
00:36:52,130 --> 00:36:53,420
Empress Mother.

403
00:36:53,420 --> 00:36:55,400
- Fifth Prince.
- Grand Uncle.

404
00:36:55,400 --> 00:36:56,890
The crown prince lost it all badly.

405
00:36:56,890 --> 00:37:00,290
Other princes just watched at a distance, but you...

406
00:37:00,290 --> 00:37:02,030
You didn't make use of this opportunity.

407
00:37:02,030 --> 00:37:05,420
But instead, you pleaded for him.

408
00:37:05,420 --> 00:37:08,180
Empress Mother, Imperial Brother is benevolent and honest.

409
00:37:08,180 --> 00:37:11,500
I believe he definitely didn't frame someone because of a power struggle.

410
00:37:11,500 --> 00:37:14,970
So, you mean you agree with the crown prince,

411
00:37:14,970 --> 00:37:18,720
that I'm truly the one who is responsible for the case of the imperial exam candidates.

412
00:37:22,180 --> 00:37:24,530
Don't be fooled by the crown prince's hypocrisy.

413
00:37:24,530 --> 00:37:27,550
The imperial court affair is not as simple as you think.

414
00:37:27,550 --> 00:37:28,910
Now the crown prince has been abolished.

415
00:37:28,910 --> 00:37:30,710
You should use this opportunity

416
00:37:30,710 --> 00:37:32,540
to impress your Emperor Father.

417
00:37:32,540 --> 00:37:35,690
Hence, you will have the chance to enter and host the Eastern Palace.

418
00:37:35,690 --> 00:37:38,800
Empress Mother, I don't like those kinds of tactics.

419
00:37:38,800 --> 00:37:41,370
And I really don't care about being the crown prince of the Eastern Palace.

420
00:37:41,370 --> 00:37:43,120
After all, Imperial Brother is my blood brother.

421
00:37:43,120 --> 00:37:46,490
He is now in danger. I absolutely won't take advantage of it.

422
00:37:54,020 --> 00:37:56,510
You really wasted all my efforts.

423
00:37:56,510 --> 00:37:59,570
Get out! I don't want to see you.

424
00:37:59,570 --> 00:38:02,590
Yes, I'll take my leave.

425
00:38:06,800 --> 00:38:10,370
Actually, Chengyin is generally a very well-behaved and obedient kid.

426
00:38:10,370 --> 00:38:13,930
Perhaps, because of what has happened to the crown prince, he has become more emotional.

427
00:38:13,930 --> 00:38:17,580
Please, Uncle, don't take it badly.

428
00:38:17,580 --> 00:38:23,490
Do you have to choose a person like the fifth prince to be the crown prince?

429
00:38:23,490 --> 00:38:26,470
Although Chengyin is not my own son,

430
00:38:26,470 --> 00:38:30,160
I diligently educated him all those years.

431
00:38:30,160 --> 00:38:32,780
I've spent a lot of effort on him.

432
00:38:32,780 --> 00:38:37,500
Uncle, please help him as much as you can.

433
00:39:17,080 --> 00:39:18,720
Go.

434
00:39:21,580 --> 00:39:23,210
Wait!

435
00:39:27,420 --> 00:39:31,910
Imperial Father, please let me go with Imperial Brother to the Western Border.

436
00:39:33,580 --> 00:39:37,070
Chengyin, what nonsense are you speaking?

437
00:39:37,070 --> 00:39:39,060
Emperor Father, you once said that

438
00:39:39,060 --> 00:39:41,110
Imperial Brother and I would get the same punishment for the same crime.

439
00:39:41,110 --> 00:39:44,090
The king's words are to be taken seriously. Emperor Father, please approve my request.

440
00:39:44,090 --> 00:39:45,740
Fifth Brother...

441
00:39:48,910 --> 00:39:52,160
Your Majesty, the fifth prince is still very young.

442
00:39:52,160 --> 00:39:54,100
He is being too emotional.

443
00:39:54,100 --> 00:39:57,090
I will teach him well after this.

444
00:40:02,680 --> 00:40:05,370
Imperial Father, Fifth Brother has always put a lot of importance on affection.

445
00:40:05,370 --> 00:40:08,070
It's understandable that he would want to accompany our imperial brother.

446
00:40:08,070 --> 00:40:09,720
It's just that beyond the Great Wall, it's not the same as the capital.

447
00:40:09,720 --> 00:40:12,130
Boundless desert, a long and far journey.

448
00:40:12,130 --> 00:40:13,690
Fifth Younger Brother has been used to comfortable living since he was younger.

449
00:40:13,690 --> 00:40:15,980
I am afraid it will be hard for him to get used to it.

450
00:40:19,310 --> 00:40:21,890
Prince Xuande is right.

451
00:40:23,420 --> 00:40:25,700
Chengyin, get up quickly.

452
00:40:25,700 --> 00:40:28,610
Don't hold up an important matter.

453
00:40:30,410 --> 00:40:34,500
Chengyin, have you thought this through?

454
00:40:34,500 --> 00:40:36,460
Imperial Father, I've made my decision.

455
00:40:36,460 --> 00:40:38,880
I want to use this chance to train in the borderlands.

456
00:40:38,880 --> 00:40:41,440
The scenery at the Western Border is beautiful. I can keep company with Imperial Brother and

457
00:40:41,440 --> 00:40:45,000
I can enrich my knowledge and also share Emperor Father's burdens.

458
00:40:53,210 --> 00:40:58,430
Since you have this intention, I approve of it.

459
00:40:58,430 --> 00:41:01,240
- Your Majesty!
- Thank you, Imperial Father!

460
00:41:04,370 --> 00:41:06,190
Have the horse ready, I'm going to the Elder Prince Zhong Manor.

461
00:41:06,190 --> 00:41:07,790
Yes.

462
00:41:09,080 --> 00:41:11,810
I'm going out of the palace, to the Minister Manor.

463
00:41:14,620 --> 00:41:19,040
Uncle, how about we put aside our plan for now?

464
00:41:19,040 --> 00:41:20,810
I worry Chengyin may get hurt.

465
00:41:20,810 --> 00:41:24,940
Although this is unexpected, it could turn out to be a good thing.

466
00:41:24,940 --> 00:41:27,120
Now the Eastern Palace is empty.

467
00:41:27,120 --> 00:41:29,650
The former crown prince will be assassinated on the journey to the west.

468
00:41:29,650 --> 00:41:34,840
Who will be the first suspect behind it?

469
00:41:35,640 --> 00:41:39,520
, Of course, it will be those princes who cast their greedy eyes on the crown prince position.

470
00:41:39,520 --> 00:41:42,170
But the fifth prince is traveling with the crown prince.

471
00:41:42,170 --> 00:41:46,620
Therefore, he will be the first one to be excluded from suspicion.

472
00:41:48,350 --> 00:41:51,190
But after all, swords can't see.

473
00:41:51,190 --> 00:41:53,110
Empress, you worry too much.

474
00:41:53,110 --> 00:41:55,570
Those sent to do the job are all highly skilled masters.

475
00:41:55,570 --> 00:41:58,890
Fifth Prince's safety is guaranteed.

476
00:41:58,890 --> 00:42:00,830
My good nephew.

477
00:42:01,850 --> 00:42:05,750
This involves the life of two princes.

478
00:42:06,480 --> 00:42:10,190
Once His Majesty gets angry and wants to do the investigation,

479
00:42:11,360 --> 00:42:13,290
I'm afraid...

480
00:42:13,290 --> 00:42:16,100
Today, I did try to stop him.

481
00:42:16,100 --> 00:42:19,760
But he is determined to get himself killed.

482
00:42:23,110 --> 00:42:28,080
Whoever tries to block my future career... will result in death.

